item.description:
Add options below to setenv or startup
&#34;-Djavax.net.ssl.trustStore=/tomcat/server.truststore -Djavax.net.ssl.trustStorePassword&#34; e.g
JAVA_OPTS=&#34;$JAVA_OPTS-Djavax.net.ssl.trustStore=${path2it}-Djavax.net.ssl.trustStorePassword=changeit&#34;

Add option to java java startup options &ldquo;-Djaavx.net.debug=all&rdquo;
Could be done with adding it to next files ${catalina.home}/bin/startup.sh ${catalina.home}/bin/setenv.sh
Or to systemctl unit file JAVA_OPTS=&quot;$JAVA_OPTS -Djavax.net.debug=all&quot;
